latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Happiest birthday to my #1 and the most beautiful girl in my life ❤️ 
I thank my stars that you walked into my life, my life would’ve been bland af without you boo. Please don’t leave me, I love you so much you mean the world to me no one can ever take your place.Thank you for being YOU, there’s no one as kind and loving as you and no one can even come close. Grateful for every second I get with you, here’s to many more together my mauzzziii I wish I was there 😘😘 You’re the best friend I could ever ask for, my sister, my family,my entertainer and drama queen❤️ enoughhhh cheezyyyy shizz gonna video call you now #themautomysum @mahickasharma

THINKING OF SUMMER – that brings with it the heat of something new. The reckless season when the air is heavy and still and your heart is racing. And you first start to care, while still knowing that seasons change.
Written, directed and edited by @itshowyoulookatit 
Featuring @thesummerjacobs @adhiraj774 
Director of Photography @sachingadankush 
Music mix @tommy8689 at @jsrstudiosofficial

Back in December 2023, I bagged my first international commercial as a lead ,all by myself. I’ve been dying to share this with you’ll 🥹 I’m so grateful to have shot for the biggest airline ever in their game changing safety commercial, you’ll are gonna see me for the next 10 years if you take an @emirates flight. So keep an eye out 🙂‍↔️ I’m the first one in the video so you won’t miss me ‼️
Super grateful for this opportunity! Special thanks to my friend and the best agent @falasteeninheels @emodelsme
